{"tid":1761688,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成績表-翠華中期業績轉蝕逾4000萬元　不派息","createTime":"2019-11-29T05:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T10:39:21.000Z","uid":283021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34f2065b5c579fff82a8732214a09ad6e3d3f8b1","tid":1761688,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"翠華控股中期業績由盈轉虧，截至9月底止，虧損4450萬港元，去年同期盈利1441萬元。業績轉虧主要由於收入大幅下跌，以及營運成本上漲所致。不派中期息。<br />\n<br />\n期內，收入8.38億元，按年減少6.4%。當中，香港收入為5.37億元，按年減少4.5%；內地收入為2.92億元，按年減少10.2%。<br />\n<br />\n至於毛利率按年減少0.9個百分點至71.2%。截至9月底，集團經營合共84家餐廳，當中香港按年淨增加5間分店至41間；中國內地按年淨增加4間至38間。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，人民幣貶值及消費氣氛轉弱，到港旅客數目大幅下降，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加上大部分餐廳因香港近期發生社會活動，臨時改變或縮短營業時間甚或關店，尤其在周末期間，均導致顧客無法惠顧，</span></span>種種不利因素對香港整個零售及餐飲業的業務及財務表現構成嚴重影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495122-20191129.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495122-20191129.htm&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLQV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=e7178083\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495122-20191129.htm&h=a3db3296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495122-20191129.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b73ad8a3fa1a14a4e691f83bc1f1dd199da45374","tid":1761688,"uid":45672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:24:38.000Z","msg":"大陸人食就得啦"},{"pid":"fab494c3a375f13dc821abedc01324a77eeedbd9","tid":1761688,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"menu完全無變過<br />\n不思進取"},{"pid":"0da35bf113c7ce754e1dc7f6b1ed2aaa5e4f1343","tid":1761688,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"去大灣區開多幾間囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hk